{"tid":2357866,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"團體轟梁家傑煽暴，促廉署徹查","createTime":"2021-01-07T17:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T17:52:46.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b5d67a4c903be5d7c2aeeaa21f9dbbe4c29215ec","tid":2357866,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T17:20:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Pu.uhNbDk19rv1dH8AKrBw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NC44/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/VeMWdDo9zI7_gVc.CHKvJA--~B/aD00Mjg7dz02MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/thesun.hk.com/386ef08d832d94d9387d11a49e808cf8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FPu.uhNbDk19rv1dH8AKrBw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NC44%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FVeMWdDo9zI7_gVc.CHKvJA--~B%2FaD00Mjg7dz02MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F386ef08d832d94d9387d11a49e808cf8&h=2c21d4e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】在反修例示威期間，公民黨主席梁家傑曾於香港大學召開的一個校長論壇上，公然聲稱「暴力有的時候是對問題的一種解決方式」，此外梁亦曾親身到美國及歐洲議會訪問，被質疑勾結外國政黨。有團體昨到北角廉政公署總部聲討梁家傑，炮轟他賣國求榮、煽動暴力活動以及收取黑金遺禍香港，促請廉署對其進行調查。<br />\n<br />\n團體東方之珠義工社團昨到廉署聲討梁家傑，他們高呼「強烈要求廉署、徹查漢奸梁家傑」、「協助暴力合法、勾結外國勢力」及「賣國求榮、黑金害死香港、市民憤怒了」等口號，該會主席何華批評，梁家傑在反修例示威期間公然宣揚暴力，令當時本已嚴峻的局勢更加火上澆油，形容其行為惡貫滿盈。他認為梁犯下的種種罪惡路人皆知，促請廉署應不偏不倚、且用透明的方式調查梁。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/團體轟梁家傑煽暴-促廉署徹查-214500023.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E8%BD%9F%E6%A2%81%E5%AE%B6%E5%82%91%E7%85%BD%E6%9A%B4-%E4%BF%83%E5%BB%89%E7%BD%B2%E5%BE%B9%E6%9F%A5-214500023.html&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z71zpTq0bGO0w7tnLPpoXkc%3D&h=18ad838e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/團體轟梁家傑煽暴-促廉署徹查-214500023.html</a>"},{"pid":"5e411bd0f2c37cc367ab79004c870ed4ad6aa4e0","tid":2357866,"uid":82938,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T17:24:39.000Z","ms